productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
My neighbor Ardeth has one of these. She works as a gasman and she says it looks fuzzy.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
